    <p>{`It must unlock `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`mutex`}</inlineCode>{` in order for `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`pthread_cond_wait()`}</inlineCode>{` routine to complete.`}</p>
    <p><inlineCode parentName="p">{`pthread_cond_broadcast()`}</inlineCode>{` routine unlocks all of the threads blocked on the condition variable.`}</p>
    <ul>
      <li parentName="ul">{`Proper locking and unlocked of mutex is essential for these routines
- Failing to lock may cause it NOT to block
- Failing to unlock the mutex may not allow a matching `}<inlineCode parentName="li">{`pthread_cond_wait()`}</inlineCode>{` routine to complete (it will remain blocked)`}</li>
    </ul>
